# AppVector MCP Server Configuration
# No environment variables needed - all authentication via Authorization header

# AUTHENTICATION:
# Provide your AppVector API token via Authorization header in MCP Inspector
# Format: "Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN" or "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"
# Obtain token from: https://appvector.io/users/get_token/

# Optional: Server port (defaults to 3000)
# PORT=3000